OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFortnite penalised after   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclaims it tricked users    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The company behind popular video game  
OL,6, Fortnite has agreed to pay $520m       
OL,7, (#427m) to settle claims from US       
OL,8, regulators that it violated child      
OL,9, privacy laws and tricked users into    
OL,10, making purchases.                      
OL,12,FThe complaint cited tactics such as a  
OL,13,Fbutton design that could trigger       
OL,14,Fpurchases while the game was loading.  
OL,16,FEpic Games said the settlement resolved
OL,17,Fconcerns about "past designs".         
OL,19,FIt said the practices were "not how    
OL,20,FFortnite operates".                    
